&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a title=&quot;Restaurant Kokkeriet&quot; href=&quot;http://www.kokkeriet.dk/en/table_booking.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;by email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@kokkeriet.dk&quot;&gt;info@kokkeriet.dk&lt;/a&gt; or by phone at +45 3315 2777.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection in the comments area to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Also in the comments section, please provide a cell phone number or local (hotel) contact number in Copenhagen. The restaurant will call you the day of the dining date to reconfirm and discuss any allergies or special needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
